## Current Implementation Status

### Frontend
**Clients (API Facades)**:
- movieClient.ts - Movies browsing, search, details, showtimes
- paymentClient.ts - Payment card CRUD
- authClient.ts - Authentication operations

**Hooks (ONE per feature)**:
- useMovies - Movie browsing with pagination
- useMovieSearch - Movie search with filters
- usePaymentCards - Payment cards with modal state and CRUD
- useUser - User profile (NOTE: Still uses direct fetch, needs refactoring to use userClient)
- useUserId - SSR-safe userId extraction (KEEP - prevents hydration errors)

**Utils**:
- auth.ts - getAuthToken(), getUserIdFromToken(), getRefreshToken()
- payment.ts - displayCardNumber(), formatExpirationDate()
- profile.ts - validatePhoneNumber(), checkPasswordSecurity()
- pagination.ts - Pagination helpers

**Reusable Components**:
- UserProfileSidebar - Profile picture + logout (used across user pages)
- UserNavTabs - Navigation tabs (profile/payments/orders)
- HomeAddressFields - Address input fields
- PaymentCardsList, PaymentCardItem - Payment UI components

### Backend
**Controllers**: Thin, delegate to services
**Services**: Thick, contain all business logic + DTO conversion
**Repositories**: Data access only

### Known Technical Debt
- useUser.ts - Should use userClient (currently direct fetch calls)
- Profile page - Could benefit from further recomponentization 

